    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that stuff is still messy, but it feels like some people say the movement's methods were actually kind of problematic or that they actually caused more division in the long run. what do you think about that? was the nonviolent approach actually the best way to go, or was it just the one that everyone agrees on now because it's easier to talk about?",
